# =============================================================================
# R/price_data.R
# Static price data and hospital registry
#
# In production this file is GENERATED by R/fetch_mrf_data.R, which downloads
# and processes each hospital's CMS machine-readable file. During development
# (or when the MRF pipeline hasn't run yet), this hand-coded version stands in.
#
# The structure mirrors exactly what fetch_mrf_data.R produces, so the app
# code never needs to change — only this data file gets replaced.
# =============================================================================

